name: Sandy / Zsanett Egerhazi / Vega Vixen
description:
A TI of Hungarian pornstar, model and modelling agency owner Zsanett Egerhazi aka Sandy Fantasy.

Given the (extremely) NSFW nature of most of the training images this embedding tends to throw up occasional NSFW images even with SFW/NSFW in the prompts/neg prompts.

Apologies if that's not something you want, this can be significantly reduced by strongly weighting -ve prompts e.g "Naked:3", but I've been unable to stop it completely. Obviously, none have been included in the examples.

modelVersions.name: v1.1
modelVersions.description: Same 200 images, 40 vectors per token, learning rate of 0.0015, but an extra 7,000 steps. Considerably better, but still not perfect.
